<a name="hw"><h3>Homework</h3></a>

<p>I'll post each assignment on the website at least one week before the due date.  As a general rule, material covered in class on Monday is fair game for the problem set due on Friday.

<p>Homework will be due every Friday in class.  If you will not be in 
class on a due date, you can turn in your homework in advance to my 
mailbox in the Math Department office, 405 Snow, or to my office, 623 
Snow.  Your homework should be as neat and legible as if it were typed, 
and all sheets should be stapled together. <b>Homework turned in late 
will not be accepted.</b>

