<a name="test"><h3>Tests</h3></a>

<p><b>Test #1</b> was given in class on <b>Friday, October 1.</b>  The test will cover chapters 1-2 of the book.
<ul>
<li><a href="review1.pdf">Detailed review information</a>
</ul>

<p><b>Test #2</b> will be given in class on <b>Friday, November 12.</b>  The test will focus on chapter 3
and sections 6.1 and 6.2.
<ul>
<li><a href="review2.pdf">Detailed review information</a>
</ul>

<p><b>The final exam</b> will be given on <b>Monday, December 13</b>, 10:30 AM - 1:00 PM.  The exam will focus on material after Test #2 (i.e.,
Section 6.3 and parts of Chapters 7 and 4), but everything covered
throughout the semester is fair game.

